o Games\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three-time world champion Daiya Seto will swim the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 200m individual medley after Japan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s swimming federation announced its 27-member team for the Paris Games on March 27.\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 675, \"end\": 685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daiya_Seto\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Daiya Seto\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daiya_Seto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daiya_Seto\"}, {\"begin\": 747, \"end\": 755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para_swimming\", \"score\": 0.9999349003623554, \"rank\": 6.510387593689057e-05, \"text\": \"swimming\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para_swimming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para_swimming\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 200m individual medley\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 730}, {\"ngram\": \"its 27-member team\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 795}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 815}, {\"ngram\": \"March\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 824}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An 18-year-old Ikee was named Most Valuable Player of the 2018 Asian Games after claiming six golds and two silvers, and was expected to be one of the stars of the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 1009, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 860, \"end\": 880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Most_valuable_player\", \"score\": 0.9999973286839331, \"rank\": 2.2815856021404363e-06, \"text\": \"Most Valuable Player\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Most_valuable_player\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Most_valuable_player\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An 18-year-old Ikee\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2018 Asian Games\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 904}, {\"ngram\": \"six golds\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"two silvers\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 945}, {\"ngram\": \"the stars\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 986}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1008}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In early 2019, a few months after those triumphs, she was diagnosed with leukaemia and spent around 10 months in hospital.\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those triumphs\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1059}, {\"ngram\": \"leukaemia\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1093}, {\"ngram\": \"around 10 months\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"hospital\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She returned to competition only in August 2020 and completed an incredible comeback by winning the 100m freestyle and 100m butterfly at the 2021 Olympic trials.\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1296, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1177}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible comeback\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1219}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m freestyle\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1249}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2021 Olympic trials\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1295}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her times were not fast enough to qualify for the individual events in Tokyo, but the performances gained her selection for both freestyle and medley relay teams at her home Olympics.\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1369, \"end\": 1374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7460016177278656e-14, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her times\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1307}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual events\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1365}, {\"ngram\": \"the performances\", \"from